      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRIKEY MATE (1) showed good early speed and led throughout to score his maiden two back then finished sixth last start and beaten 8 lengths at Broken Hill over 375m (22.70). Yet to win here but has run some good races. Likely to improve sharply this time. MY LITTLE LUCY (4) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at Broken Hill over 525m behind State Of Madness (31.54) in a Grade 5. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. ELLA'S DESTINY (5) is usually quickly into stride. Last start finished 4th in a Other on May 19 over 342m at this track behind Blue Energy beaten 6 lengths (20.05). With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts CORRYONG (2) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
